curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/6466' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8251", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8251 is a single, low noise and high precision  operational amplifier optimized for high voltage operation  from 4.5V to 36V single supply. The device provides  rail-to-rail output operation.  The SGM8251 offers a low offset voltage less than  18μV and a low bias current. The combination of  characteristics makes the SGM8251 a good choice for  temperature measurements, pressure and position  sensors,  strain  gauge  amplifiers  and  medical  instrumentation, or any other 4.5V to 36V applications  requiring precision and long-term stability.  The SGM8251 is available in Green SOT-23-5, SOIC-8  and MSOP-8 packages. It is rated over the -40℃ to +125℃  temperature range.      "}'
